Planet korr, definys gans [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek]], yw korf nevek ow resa a-dro an howl<ref name="finalresolution">{{cite news|url=http://www.iau.org/static/resolutions/Resolution_GA26-5-6.pdf|format=PDF|title=Definition of a Planet in the Solar System: Resolutions 5 and 6|date=2006-08-24|work=IAU 2006 General Assembly|publisher=International Astronomical Union|accessdate=2008-01-26}}</ref> neb yw gronnedhek lowr dhos ha bos pelyek awos gravedh y honan mes na re klerhas y ranndir a planetesimalys, ha nyns yw loor. <ref name="iau">{{cite news|publisher=International Astronomical Union|title=IAU 2006 General Assembly: Result of the IAU Resolution votes|url=http://www.iau.org/iau0603.414.0.html|year=2006|accessdate=2008-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/profile.cfm?Object=Dwarf|title=Dwarf Planets|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2008-01-22}}</ref> Yma edhomm dhodho gronnedh lowr dhe fedha y nerth gwaskek ha drehedhes komposter hydrostatyk. 

An hanow "planet korr" a veu adoptys yn 2006 yn unn glassans korfow ow resea a-dro an howl yn teyr rann. Yth esa moghheans yn diskudhansow taklennow treus-Nevyon neb a gesstrivyas erbynn [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]] yn braster, hag yn gortiwedh an diskudhans Eris<ref name="mass"/>, taklenn gans moy a ronnedh es [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]]. An klassans a lever bos korfow gronnedhek lowr dhe glerhe ranndir aga resekva gelwys "planetys", hag an re nag yw gronnedhek lowr dhe dhos ha bos pelyek awos gravedh y honan bos gelwys "korfow byghan system howlek". Yntredha, yma planetys korr. An styryans adoptys yn sodhogel gans an [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] re veu lawa hag arvreusys, ha disputys gans godhonydhyon kepar hag Alan Stern. <ref name="Stern">{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/5283956.stm|title=Pluto vote 'hijacked' in revolt|publisher=BBC News|first=Paul|last=Rincon|date=2006-08-25|accessdate=2008-01-26}}</ref><ref name="Stern2009">{{cite web|date=2009-11-30|title=Alan Stern: â€˜A Chihuahua is still a dog, and Pluto is still a planet'|publisher=EarthSky (Earthsky Interviews)|author=Jorge Salazar|url=http://www.earthsky.org/interviewpost/space/alan-stern-%E2%80%98a-chihuahua-is-still-a-dog-and-pluto-is-still-a-planet|accessdate=2009-12-08}}</ref>

An [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] a aswonn pymp planetys korr y'n termyn ma; [[Ceres]], [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]], [[Haumea]], [[Makemake]] ha [[Eris]]<ref name="WGPSN"/>. Dew hepken, [[Ceres]] ha [[Pluton]] re veu mires yn ta lowr dhe brevi aga bos pelyek lowr ha kewera an styryans. Steronydhyon a grys [[Eris]] yw pelyek lowr drefenn y vos brassa y ronnedh es [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]]. Diwettha, an [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] a erviras res yw taklennow treus-Nevyon heb hanow gans myns pur golowa es +1 (ha dredho braster kalkys gans awrgym  moy ages 838 km <ref name="bruton">{{cite web|title=Conversion of Absolute Magnitude to Diameter for Minor Planets|publisher=Department of Physics & Astronomy (Stephen F. Austin State University)|author=Dan Bruton|url=http://www.physics.sfasu.edu/astro/asteroids/sizemagnitude.html|accessdate=2008-06-13}}</ref>))bos henwys yn-dann desev planetys korr yns.

Gogrysys yw moy ages dew ugens taklennow aswonnys erell yn system howlek yw planetys korr, ha bys dew kans planetys korr yn ranndir gelwys [[grogys Kuiper]]. <ref name="Brown"/>

